                    "line_text": "Oh !… je ne pose pas pour ça,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Du tout… mais… permettez, Madame,",
