                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "Que de prime abord il n’a l’air.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "Ses deux majuscules Ggé. Nène.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "Qui font songer à la Géhenne",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "Semblent les Portes de l’Enfer !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Tu vois comme cela s’arrange.\nCe nom, au fond, est moins étrange\nQue de prime abord il n’a l’air.\nSes deux majuscules Ggé. Nène.\nQui font songer à la Géhenne\nSemblent les Portes de l’Enfer !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "Eh, bien !… mes mains ne sont pas fortes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "Mais Moi, je fermerai ces Portes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 51,
                    "line_text": "Qui ne laisseront plus filtrer",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 52,
                    "line_text": "Le moindre rayon de lumière,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 53,
                    "line_text": "Je les fermerai de manière",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 54,
                    "line_text": "Qu’on ne puisse jamais entrer.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Eh, bien !… mes mains ne sont pas fortes,\nMais Moi, je fermerai ces Portes,\nQui ne laisseront plus filtrer\nLe moindre rayon de lumière,\nJe les fermerai de manière\nQu’on ne puisse jamais entrer."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 10,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 55,
                    "line_text": "En jouant sur le mot Géhenne,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 56,
                    "line_text": "J’ai, semble-t-il dire, la Haine,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 57,
                    "line_text": "Et je ne l’ai pas à moitié,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 58,
                    "line_text": "Je l’ai, je la tiens, la Maudite !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 59,
                    "line_text": "Je la tiens bien, et toute, et vite,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 60,
                    "line_text": "Je veux l’étrangler sans pitié !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "En jouant sur le mot Géhenne,\nJ’ai, semble-t-il dire, la Haine,\nEt je ne l’ai pas à moitié,\nJe l’ai, je la tiens, la Maudite !\nJe la tiens bien, et toute, et vite,\nJe veux l’étrangler sans pitié !"
        },
        {
